<plot>The trials and tribulations of the underappreciated and uncelebrated father-of-the-bride are depicted in flashback from the day of the ceremony. His bewilderment at his daughter's choice of beau, his exclusion from important events such as the shower, and his delegation to such menial tasks as addressing the invitations are depicted.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?558840</url></doc>
